sourceDetail: TikTok direct message after viral video
notes: Very interested in K-Beauty glass skin products. Active on TikTok with 150K followers. Wants to create content around products.
recommendedAction: Convert to account immediately. High engagement potential. Offer influencer partnership.

notes: Premium spa interested in organic and clean beauty products. Referral from existing client.
recommendedAction: Schedule in-person meeting. Offer product samples and training.

notes: Makeup studio for events and weddings. Looking for professional makeup lines. Active on Instagram with engaged followers.
recommendedAction: Send makeup artist samples. Offer training workshop.

notes: Inquiry about clean and natural beauty products. Small retail space in Subang Jaya.
recommendedAction: Follow up with detailed product catalog. Emphasize certifications.

notes: Nail salon interested in expanding to skincare. Small budget but growing.
recommendedAction: Offer starter package with payment plan.

notes: TikTok Shop seller with strong sales. Looking for exclusive trending products. Fast-moving inventory.
recommendedAction: Priority lead. Offer exclusive first access to trending items.

notes: Aesthetic clinic looking for medical-grade skincare products. High-end clientele.
recommendedAction: Schedule consultation meeting. Provide clinical data.

notes: Hair salon focused on coloring and treatments. Budget-conscious. Needs convincing on value.
recommendedAction: Provide samples. Emphasize profit margins and client satisfaction.

notes: Online beauty retailer with Shopee and Lazada stores. Looking for wholesale partnership.
recommendedAction: Offer wholesale pricing and dropship options.

notes: Wellness-focused spa interested in natural and botanical products. Met at recent trade show in Penang.
recommendedAction: Follow up with wellness-focused product line presentation.

notes: Express beauty bar for quick treatments. Looking for fast-acting products. High turnover.
recommendedAction: Offer trial sizes and quick-result products.

notes: High-end salon specializing in Italian beauty techniques. Decided to import directly from Italy.
recommendedAction: Lost to direct import. Follow up in 6 months.

notes: Medical aesthetics clinic. Looking for professional-grade anti-aging products. High-value potential client.
recommendedAction: High-value lead. Schedule detailed consultation with technical expert.

notes: Beauty studio targeting teenagers and young adults. Looking for affordable, trending products.
recommendedAction: Focus on trending, affordable products. Offer social media collaboration.

notes: Beauty training academy needs products for student training. Bulk orders for classes.
recommendedAction: Offer education pricing and training support materials.

notes: Wellness center incorporating beauty services. Strong focus on clean, sustainable products.
recommendedAction: Emphasize certifications and sustainability credentials.

notes: Makeup service for events. Small operation with limited budget. Needs education on product quality.
recommendedAction: Provide samples and educational materials. Payment plan option.

notes: High-end beauty lounge in Pavilion. Looking for exclusive luxury brands. Premium clientele willing to pay premium prices.
recommendedAction: Priority lead. Offer exclusive brands and VIP service.

notes: Retail store focusing on natural and organic products. Small but growing business in Georgetown.
recommendedAction: Send clean beauty catalog. Emphasize natural ingredients.

notes: Beauty subscription box service similar to Ipsy. Looking for exclusive products for curated boxes. Active TikTok presence.
recommendedAction: Excellent opportunity. Offer sample sizes and exclusive products.
